reviewText: If you're a Felicity fan or just someone who enjoys the eighteenth century in general, this is a fun thing to have in your collection. I would recommend it especially for kids, but it is too short and the cover led me to believe it was a tie-in for the Felicity movie, which it wasn't-- more oriented to the Felicity books on which the movie is based. Good for kids, I say, just too short!
